snippet: Australia's central bank kept its cash rate steady at a record low of 2.5 percent on Tuesday, a widely expected decision given evidence past policy cuts were working to stimulate the economy as desired....

headline.print_headline: Australia Central Bank Holds Rates at 2.5 Percent
headline.main: Australia Central Bank Holds Rates at 2.5 Percent

lead_paragraph: Australia's central bank kept its cash rate steady at a record low of 2.5 percent on Tuesday, a widely expected decision given evidence past policy cuts were working to stimulate the economy as desired.
